olive oil
1 packet beef mince
1 bag Soffritto Mix
1 sachet Herb & Mushroom Seasoning
1 sachet Chicken-Style Stock Powder
1 tin tinned cherry tomatoes
1 packet Pumpkin, Sundried Tomato & Feta Ravioloni
1 packet Grated Parmesan Cheese
1 bag rocket

• Boil the kettle
• Heat a frying pan over high heat
with olive oil. Cook beef mince and
soffritto mix, breaking up with a
spoon, until browned, 3 mins
• Add seasoning, stock, tinned
tomatoes and a drizzle of water and
cook, until reduced, 3-5 mins

• Pour boiling water into a saucepan
over medium-low heat
• Simmer raviolini until ‘al dente’,
3 mins
• Using a slotted spoon, transfer
raviolini to frying pan. Toss to coat
in sauce

• In a bowl, combine rocket and a
drizzle of oil. Season to taste
• Plate up raviolini and sauce
• Top with rocket and Parmesan